# Hotel Management System — Walkthrough

## What Was Built

A comprehensive **Hotel Management System** for a single property with 3 room types, built as a Next.js/TypeScript application.

---

## Pages & Features

| Page | Features |
|------|----------|
| **Dashboard** | KPIs (Occupancy, In-house guests, Arrivals, Departures, Revenue), today's arrivals/departures, alerts, room breakdown, recent bookings |
| **Bookings** | Month calendar view (color-coded by room type) + list view, create/edit/delete bookings, meal plan & status |
| **Quick Check-in** | 3-step wizard: search guest → verify profile → assign room + meal plan → QR key success screen |
| **Guests** | Full guest profiles (passport, DOB, nationality, loyalty tier, dietary pref, VIP flag), booking history, stats |
| **Room Types** | CRUD with 20+ attributes per room, amenity picker |
| **Meal Plans** | EP / CP / MAP / AP cards with meal inclusions, dietary accommodations, adoption stats |
| **Housekeeping** | Color-coded room board (Clean/Dirty/Inspected/DND/Out-of-Order), click-to-edit, staff workload |
| **Maintenance** | Issue tracker with priority/status/assignment, quick-resolve button |
| **Pricing** | Base + weekend + seasonal pricing + Airbnb-style smart discount rules |
| **Availability** | Room inventory, min/max stay, blackout dates |
| **Amenity Manager** | Category + facility CRUD |
| **Hotel Overview** | Core hotel info editor |

**Smart Search (`Ctrl+K`)**: Global overlay searching across bookings, guests, and rooms.

---

## File Structure Created

```
app/
├── page.tsx                    # Main shell, sidebar, all state, routing
├── components/
│   ├── types.ts                # Shared TypeScript interfaces
│   ├── ui.tsx                  # Shared primitives (GlobalStyles, icons, Btn, Badge, etc.)
│   ├── Dashboard.tsx           # Dashboard page
│   ├── Bookings.tsx            # Calendar + list view
│   ├── CheckIn.tsx             # Quick check-in wizard
│   ├── Customers.tsx           # Guest management
│   ├── MealPlans.tsx           # Meal plan management
│   ├── Housekeeping.tsx        # HK board
│   └── Maintenance.tsx         # Maintenance tracker
└── api/
    ├── bookings/route.ts       # Full CRUD
    ├── customers/route.ts      # Full CRUD
    ├── pricing-rules/route.ts  # CRUD
    ├── housekeeping/route.ts   # GET + PUT
    ├── maintenance/route.ts    # GET + POST + PUT
    ├── meal-plans/route.ts     # GET
    └── seed/route.ts           # Populates dummy data
```

